OL,11,FThere previously had been some
OL,12,Fwrangling by unions and businesses
OL,13,Fover the contents of the Bill, but the
OL,14,Fgovernment say they've struck a
OL,15,Fbalance between security for working
OL,16,Fpeople and flexibility for businesses.
