OL,3,CMillions of workers to get new rights
OL,4,Cfrom day one in job under new law
OL,6,FSome measures, such as the right to
OL,7,F"switch off" at the end of a working
OL,8,Fday, are not in the Bill but will be
OL,9,Fincluded in a so-called "Next Steps"
OL,10,Fdocument for further consideration and
OL,11,Fconsultation.
OL,13,FThere will be consultations on a new
OL,14,Fstatutory period, with ministers
OL,15,Fpromising employers a "lighter touch"
OL,16,Fprocess covering dismissals. It's
OL,17,Funderstood the government would like
OL,18,Fthis period to be nine months.
