OL,6,FWorkers on those contracts will now be
OL,7,Fentitled to a "reasonable" number of
OL,8,Fshifts and financial compensation if a
OL,9,Fshift is cancelled or cut short.
OL,11,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner
OL,12,Fsaid the plan "to make work pay is
OL,13,Fcentral to achieving our growth
OL,14,Fmission, boosting productivity".
OL,16,F"After years of stagnation under the
OL,17,FTories, we're replacing a race to the
OL,18,Fbottom with a race to the top, so
OL,19,Femployers compete on innovation and
OL,20,Fquality."
